'''Bridei''' ([[Scottish Gaelic]]: ''Bridei'') son of [[Uurad of the Picts|Uurad]]  was [[king of the Picts]], in modern [[Scotland]], in c. [[842]]. Two of his brothers, [[Ciniod II of the Picts|Ciniod]] and [[Drest X of the Picts|Drest]], are also said, in the king lists of the [[Pictish Chronicle]], to have reigned for a short time.

